songs.lyrics:
A empty vessel
Travles the world
With no where to go
And no where to be
His mind is free but his body stuck
He screams and screams
But no one answers
He looks down at death and leans forward
He knows about the dangers but he dosen’t care
His life has been way to hard
He dares himself to take the step
And just like that, ther’s nothing left
songs.title: Empty vessel
